            "code": "  // 新建普通变更建议/变更指令（包括批量）\n  sysWizardECMNewDetailAction(event: EventInterface): void {\n    const wizardCom = WizardEventUtil.getWizardCom(event);\n    // const button = this.getExeCom<DppButtonComponent>(event);\n    // const action = button.getUiModel().action!;\n    const formComOfWizard = wizardCom.getWizardHeadInstance<DppFormComponent>(0);\n    const formData = formComOfWizard.getNotTranFormData<IFoundaton>();\n\n    if (formData[SystemClassFieldEnum.ISCHECKOUT] !== 'Y') {\n      // guess ? table!.setLoading(false) : this.setLoading(event, false);\n      this.message.warning('backend.business.message.notCheckout');\n      return;\n    }\n    EcmEventUtil.createDetailObject(event, formData, this.ecm, this.message);\n    // const modal = CommonEventUtil.buildDefaultModal<DppGlobalSearchComponent>(event, (okButtonThis, advCom) => {\n    //   okButtonThis.loading = true;\n    //   this.setLoading(event, true);\n    //   // const isValid = formComponent.onSubmit();\n    //   const selectDatas = advCom.table.getSelectedItems();\n    //   if (selectDatas.length > 0) {\n    //     const master = {\n    //       classGuid: formComOfWizard.getNotTranFormData<IBaseData>()[SystemClassFieldEnum.CLASSGUID],\n    //       guid: formComOfWizard.getNotTranFormData<IBaseData>()[SystemClassFieldEnum.GUID],\n    //       procrtGuid: formComOfWizard.getNotTranFormData<IBaseData>()['PROCESS']['GUID'],\n    //       isBatch: action['isBatch']\n    //     };\n    //     // let objects = [formComponent.getFormData<IFoundaton>()];\n    //     // if (formComponent.dppRender.mode === ModeTypeEnum.BATCHCREATE) {\n    //     //   objects = formComponent.getFormData<IFoundaton[]>();\n    //     // }\n    //     const items = new Array<{ GUID$: string; CLASSGUID$: string }>();\n    //     selectDatas.forEach(item => {\n    //       items.push({\n    //         GUID$: item.GUID$,\n    //         CLASSGUID$: item['CLASSGUID$']\n    //       });\n    //     });\n    //     this.ecm.createDetailObject(master, items).subscribe(\n    //       res => {\n    //         if (res.success && res.data) {\n    //           if (res.data.totalCnt === res.data.successCnt) {\n    //             this.message.success('common.operation.newSuccess');\n    //           } else {\n    //             this.message.createTableMessage('success', 'common.operation.newSuccess', res.data);\n    //           }\n    //           this.contentComCallback(\n    //             event,\n    //             CommonEventUtil.buildCallBack(res.data, undefined, EventCallbacksActionName.UPDATE)\n    //           );\n    //           modal.close();\n    //         } else {\n    //           this.message.warning(`${res.errorCode}:${res.errorMsg}`);\n    //         }\n    //         okButtonThis.loading = false;\n    //         this.setLoading(event, false);\n    //       },\n    //       err => {\n    //         okButtonThis.loading = false;\n    //         this.setLoading(event, false);\n    //       }\n    //     );\n    //   } else {\n    //     this.message.warning('common.operation.noDataSelect');\n    //     okButtonThis.loading = false;\n    //     this.setLoading(event, false);\n    //   }\n    // });\n  }"
